OL,6,FKnown as Radical Jack, he died in 1840
OL,7,Fat the age of 48, prompting the
OL,8,Fcommunity to raise the funds needed to
OL,9,Ferect the monument, which opened four
OL,10,Fyears later in 1844.
OL,12,F'It is possible to see as far as the
OL,13,FCleveland Hills in the south and the
OL,14,FCheviots to the north'
OL,16,FBased on the Temple of Hephaestus in
OL,17,FAthens, the monument is 70ft high,
OL,18,F100ft long and has columns more than
OL,19,F6ft wide.
