OL,6,FFrom the top, it is possible to see as
OL,7,Ffar as the Cleveland Hills in the
OL,8,Fsouth and the Cheviots to the north.
OL,10,FGed Parker, a volunteer from the
OL,11,FNational Trust, which looks after the
OL,12,Fsite, said: "The trend at the time was
OL,13,Fto rediscover and copy what the
OL,14,Fancients had done, particularly in
OL,15,FGreece and Rome."
